    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "hi @Haroenv,\r\nThanks for your quick feedback.\r\nAfter further testing, it happens that some times it works (but most of the time its not) but Im not able to figure out why. \r\nAnd yes I noticed that the sub-level should be filled once a first level value is refined.\r\n\r\nAlso I forget to mention that Im using the onMount svelte hook cause I'm in a SSR environment with Sapper and as instantsearch.js is not supporting SSR, I have to import it only on the frontend side which is done by the onMount. \r\n\r\nI come back to you with a sandbox ;) Thanks again. \r\n",
