    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "I was just going to suggest calling start after the widget has been mounted. Something seems to go wrong tick-wise with this set of tools together where you add a hierarchical widget and it seems like the `render` is called before the widget is added / before the result of its call is in. It can be solved by doing:\r\n\r\n```\r\nsetTimeout(() => {\r\n  search.start();\r\n}, 0);\r\n```\r\n\r\nNote also you need to `preventDefault` the click on the event: https://codesandbox.io/s/svelte-forked-5e9d3?file=/hierarchical-list.svelte",
    "created_at": "2020-10-22T13:45:26Z",
    "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/issues/4543#issuecomment-714504821",
