    "body": "Ok finally figured out the problem.\r\nIt's because I have on the same view a menu widget (the single level one) using the same attribute (hierarchical_categories_en.lvl0) than the hierarchical menu. \r\nIs that a bug or is it my UX implementation that shouldn't exist having those 2 widgets in parallel  😅 ? ",
